Object definition 

1) Everything is an object.
2) Object sending u messages.
3) Composed of other objects.
4) "Type".
5) Same type can handle some messages. 

Classes

1) Class in C++ same as struct in C.
2) Access specifiers are 3 in C++ - private(default),public,protected.
3) Interface are the data and methods in the access-specifiers.
4) cout,cin,cerr in C++.
